	This update brings the bee hive node and honey comb textures!

  Also honey drops, for attracting bees in the baitbox.
</p>

<h3 class="bg0 fg1 ph3 pv2 mb3">Nodes</h3>
<div>
  <%= render_node.("yatm_bees:bee_hive") %>
</div>

<h3 class="bg0 fg1 ph3 pv2 mb3">Craft-items</h3>
<div>
  <%= render_craftitem.("yatm_bees:honey_drop") %>
  <%= render_craftitem.("yatm_bees:honey_comb") %>
